  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_38_9",
    "text": "①特点：俄罗斯交通部门齐全，铁路、公路、航空、内河、海洋和管道运输均很 发达，以铁路运输为主。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.100418410041841,
      0.5909838762750905,
      0.9409576940957695,
      0.6456071076011846
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_38",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_38_10",
    "text": "②分布：欧洲部分(非常密集，以莫斯科为中心呈放射状)和亚洲部分(比较稀疏。 但有一条非常重要的铁路—亚欧大陆桥)的分市不平衡。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10413761041376104,
      0.6541625534715367,
      0.9381682938168294,
      0.7087857847976308
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_38",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_38_11",
    "text": "③河运：伏尔加河",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17387261738726173,
      0.7193155643303718,
      0.34774523477452346,
